As described in
https://github.com/microsoft/onnxruntime/issues/8556
onnx can not be used with onnx_runtime with enabled schema static registration.

We solve this issue by disabling assertion and additional onnx ops registration in onnx_runtime.
For detailed description, see
https://st.yandex-team.ru/DTCC-1398

--- contrib/libs/onnx/onnx/defs/schema.cc	(index)
+++ contrib/libs/onnx/onnx/defs/schema.cc	(working tree)
@@ -1563,7 +1563,7 @@ OpName_Domain_Version_Schema_Map& OpSchemaRegistry::map() {
       // Invoke register of experimental operators.
       RegisterOnnxPreviewOperatorSetSchema();
 
-#ifndef NDEBUG
+#if 0
       size_t dbg_registered_schema_count = GetRegisteredSchemaCount() - dbg_initial_schema_count;
       // Check enabled only if schemas for all opset versions are loaded
       if (OpSchemaRegistry::Instance()->GetLoadedSchemaVersion() == 0) {
